* Third-Party Libraries

This software uses the following third-party libraries:

- **Boost.Dll**
  - simplify plugin development using C++ in a portable cross-platform manner
  - [[https://www.boost.org/][Boost official site]]
  - [[https://www.boost.org/users/license.html][Boost Software License]]

- **Boost.Locale**
  - high quality localization facilities in C++
  - [[https://www.boost.org/][Boost official site]]
  - [[https://www.boost.org/users/license.html][Boost Software License]]

- **CLI11**
  - command line parser for C++11
  - [[https://github.com/CLIUtils/CLI11][CLI11 github repository]]
  - [[https://github.com/CLIUtils/CLI11?tab=License-1-ov-file#readme][CLI11 License]]

$0